transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling. This is John. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, John. I just went online and ordered 10 of these new Viagra pills that you're offering.

Speaker 1: And it said that I was supposed to get a price of $49.

Speaker 2: But when I went to the receipt section, it says the charge is $63.95.

Speaker 1: Okay. What's your name and zip code? I can pull up your account.

Speaker 2: First name is Alan, A-L-A-N. Last name is Miller.

Speaker 1: I can give you my order number if you want that.

Speaker 2: No, the zip code's fine.

Speaker 1: 9-5-0-7-0.

Speaker 2: Thank you. One second.

Speaker 1: What was your first name again, sir?

Speaker 2: No problem. It's John.

Speaker 1: John. Thanks.

Speaker 2: Okay. Alan, you're in Saratoga?

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Okay. Yeah, I do see your order here. That went through successfully.

Speaker 1: You should have gotten a new customer price of that $49 like you said.

Speaker 2: So I'll just refund you the difference there of $14.95.

Speaker 1: Oh, okay. Oh, thanks, man. You're awesome.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so it'll take a few days. You're welcome, sir.

Speaker 1: It'll take a few days for you to see it, but I did take care of that for you.

Speaker 2: And then your order's all set, though.

Speaker 1: Okay, so I should see it in the next couple weeks?

Speaker 2: Probably about a week.

Speaker 1: Five to seven days is the usual time frame.

Speaker 2: John, they're not paying you enough, man.

Speaker 1: I appreciate your help.

Speaker 2: Of course. Have a good night, sir.

Speaker 1: Do I tell anybody what a great job you're doing?

Speaker 2: I mean, if you want to, I don't know.

Speaker 1: I guess you could send us an e-mail.

Speaker 2: But if you want to speak to me going forward, my extension is 0026.

Speaker 1: 00-what was that?

Speaker 2: 26.

Speaker 1: Okay, man. I didn't have it.

Speaker 2: Well, you're awesome, dude. Thank you, sir.

Speaker 1: You're welcome. Of course. Have a good day.

Speaker 2: You too. Thanks.
